title: What are some songs that talk about feeling out of this world? - Quora

response.answer_text: “Walking in Space,” from Hair:  “Love, I Hear,” from A Funny Thing Happened on the Way to the Forum:  “Out of This World,” from Out of This World:  “In Paradisum,” from Faure’s Requiem:  “Losing My Mind,” from Follies:  “Mild und Leise,” the Liebestod from Tristan und Isolde:

I'm in love with a wonderful guy...by Rogers and Hammerstein, sung by Mitzi Gaynor.On the street where you live. I'm the luckiest girl in the whole USA.I've got the sun in the morning and the moon at night.Oh what a beautiful morning, oh what a beautiful day.I'm looking over a four leaf clover that I over looked before.These are a few of my favorite thingsEvery thing is tickety boo, tickety boo..tickety boo ...sung by Danny Kaye
